data.description: Welcome to this stunning 1809 SqFt colonial in Romulus, built in 1997. This home boasts 4 spacious bedrooms, including a luxurious Master suite with a walk-in closet. Enjoy the elegance of vaulted ceilings and floor-to-ceiling windows in all bedrooms, the dining room, and the living room, creating a bright and airy atmosphere throughout. Kitchen with breakfast nook opens up to a  second-floor balcony offering a perfect spot to unwind. Convenience meets comfort with a first-floor bedroom and an adjacent bathroom, as well as a first-floor laundry area. The exterior showcases an attached 2-car garage, a fully privacy-fenced yard with a covered patio, a pool, and even a trampoline – all included with this exceptional property. Perfectly situated near the Gateway Golf Course and Romulus Elementary School, this home provides a great location for both leisure and education. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your dream home! ***OPEN HOUSES FRIDAY, SATURDAY & SUNDAY, Feb 2nd,3rd & 4th!***
